2:1 su oun, teknon mou, endunamou en th cariti th en cristw
 ihsou,
2:2 kai a hkousav par emou dia pollwn marturwn, tauta parayou
 pistoiv anyrwpoiv, oitinev ikanoi esontai kai eterouv didaxai.
2:3 su oun kakopayhson wv kalov stratiwthv ihsou cristou.
2:4 oudeiv strateuomenov empleketai taiv tou biou pragmateiaiv,
 ina tw stratologhsanti aresh.
2:5 ean de kai aylh tiv, ou stefanoutai, ean mh nomimwv
 aylhsh.
2:6 ton kopiwnta gewrgon dei prwton twn karpwn metalambanein.
2:7 noei a legw: dwh gar soi o kuriov sunesin en pasin.
2:8 mnhmoneue ihsoun criston eghgermenon ek nekrwn, ek spermatov
 dauid, kata to euaggelion mou,
2:9 en w kakopayw mecri desmwn wv kakourgov: all o logov
 tou yeou ou dedetai.
2:10 dia touto panta upomenw dia touv eklektouv, ina kai
 autoi swthriav tucwsin thv en cristw ihsou meta doxhv aiwniou.
2:11 pistov o logov: ei gar sunapeyanomen, kai suzhsomen:
2:12 ei upomenomen, kai sumbasileusomen: ei arnoumeya, kakeinov
 arnhsetai hmav:
2:13 ei apistoumen, ekeinov pistov menei: arnhsasyai
 eauton ou dunatai.

2:14 tauta upomimnhske, diamarturomenov enwpion tou kuriou
 mh logomacein eiv ouden crhsimon, epi katastrofh twn akouontwn.
2:15 spoudason seauton dokimon parasthsai tw yew, ergathn
 anepaiscunton, oryotomounta ton logon thv alhyeiav.
2:16 tav de bebhlouv kenofwniav periistaso: epi pleion gar
 prokoqousin asebeiav,
2:17 kai o logov autwn wv gaggraina nomhn exei: wn estin
 umenaiov kai filhtov,
2:18 oitinev peri thn alhyeian hstochsan, legontev thn anastasin
 hdh gegonenai, kai anatrepousin thn tinwn pistin.
2:19 o mentoi stereov yemeliov tou yeou esthken, ecwn thn
 sfragida tauthn: egnw kuriov touv ontav autou: kai: aposthtw
 apo adikiav pav o onomazwn to onoma kuriou.
2:20 en megalh de oikia ouk estin monon skeuh crusa kai argura,
 alla kai xulina kai ostrakina, kai a men eiv timhn, a de
 eiv atimian.
2:21 ean oun tiv ekkayarh eauton apo toutwn, estai skeuov
 eiv timhn, hgiasmenon kai eucrhston tw despoth, eiv pan ergon
 agayon htoimasmenon.
2:22 tav de newterikav epiyumiav feuge, diwke de dikaiosunhn,
 pistin, agaphn, eirhnhn meta twn epikaloumenwn ton kurion
 ek kayarav kardiav.
2:23 tav de mwrav kai apaideutouv zhthseiv paraitou, eidwv
 oti gennwsin macav:
2:24 doulon de kuriou ou dei macesyai, all hpion einai prov
 pantav, didaktikon, anexikakon,
2:25 en praothti paideuonta touv antidiatiyemenouv, mhpote
 dw autoiv o yeov metanoian eiv epignwsin alhyeiav,
2:26 kai ananhqwsin ek thv tou diabolou pagidov, ezwgrhmenoi
 up autou eiv to ekeinou yelhma.

3:1 touto de ginwske, oti en escataiv hmeraiv ensthsontai
 kairoi calepoi:
3:2 esontai gar oi anyrwpoi filautoi, filarguroi, alazonev,
 uperhfanoi, blasfhmoi, goneusin apeiyeiv, acaristoi, anosioi,
3:3 astorgoi, aspondoi, diaboloi, akrateiv, anhmeroi, afilagayoi,
3:4 prodotai, propeteiv, tetufwmenoi, filhdonoi mallon h
 filoyeoi,
3:5 econtev morfwsin eusebeiav, thn de dunamin authv hrnhmenoi.
 kai toutouv apotrepou.
3:6 ek toutwn gar eisin oi endunontev eiv tav oikiav kai
 aicmalwtizontev gunaikaria seswreumena amartiaiv, agomena
 epiyumiaiv poikilaiv,
3:7 pantote manyanonta kai mhdepote eiv epignwsin alhyeiav
